Package model

Class Cinema

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Cinema
  • public class Cinema
extends java.lang.Object
    Cinema object that contains details specific to each cinema. Eg. number of rows and columns of seats in the cinema, total number of seats and a unique CinemaID
    Since:
    2019-11-09
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
